{"tid":2292550,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"中大畢業生涉嫌干犯香港國安法 國家安全處已接手處理","createTime":"2020-11-19T14:35:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-20T07:45:34.000Z","uid":225931,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"41458469805c8d8d9abb66b11d2a3fb575ebbeed","tid":2292550,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T14:35:11.000Z","msg":"中文大學因應新冠疫情取消把畢業禮改為網上舉行，幾十名畢業生今日（19日）在香港中文大學校園內遊行，其間展示「光復香港，時代革命」的橫額和旗幟、叫喊「港獨」口號，涉嫌干犯《香港國安法》，更有部分人沿途以噴漆作刑事毁壞。校方已就事件報警。<br />\n<br />\n對於有人在大學校園內公然違反《香港國安法》及進行刑事毀壞，警方高度重視，並予以嚴厲譴責。警務處國家安全處已接手處理並展開調查。"},{"pid":"fbeca2021ebb94f677aa0922f74fa68fe04f999e","tid":2292550,"uid":102078,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T14:36:20.000Z","msg":"國安第一單大project<br />\n響朵靠今次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb60c14e71f76460fc84bebfe554bd44c714207f","tid":2292550,"uid":370010,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T14:36:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9b5f0e0cd8379b46c40df17a2c2b459cc76d878c","tid":2292550,"uid":112747,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T14:40:05.000Z","msg":"仲要中大報警<br />\n直接俾個畢業名單d狗<br />\n劃走邊d冇戴口罩即刻搞掂"},{"pid":"bfb6d653896f6153de49ed9dacefdcf1d5542a5f","tid":2292550,"uid":209644,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T14:42:37.000Z","msg":"中大手足 清理物品 務必小心"},{"pid":"4be41f2149129af1e41bea5037356bd826c8a0b1","tid":2292550,"uid":310817,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T14:49:04.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8b49680e4d959fa10dbd7c840b168c73c393503","tid":2292550,"uid":29836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-20T07:45:34.000Z","msg":"得架喇知架喇死去po ig story拎光環啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" cl